"M Plus" provides live streaming of various sports events, such as live matches of Serie A, Bundesliga, Ligue 1, FA Cup, Primeira Liga, A- League, K League 1, Thai League 1, AFC Asian Qualifiers, AFC Champions League, AFC Cup, American National Basketball Association and Australian National Basketball League. 

Contents:

Live streaming in High Definition/Standard Definition offered;
Cantonese/Mandarin/English/Spanish/Japanese commentary provided; 
Please contact Customer Service for more details; 
M Plus is only available for users in Macao. 

